                       ==[ About this branch ]==

I originally was working on this project as a cmdline/unix tool, but
have decided -- as of 2018/10/08 anyway -- to pursue it as a WPF tool
instead.  Thus, I am putting the original code in a lua-code branch so
as never to lose it, and starting over in a fresh orphan master branch.



                        ==[ ULTIMA V ~ TOOLS ]==

This is a set of utilities I used for playing around with the file
formats in Ultima V: Warriors of Destiny.  In my opinion, it was the
greatest entry in the series.


